g.text: Return to city C (expand or refuel)
[1] Pick the same city every step of the route unless conditions changed. Pick the easiest to access and expand.
[2] Prefer being able to expand in the last step.
[4] Not checking 'will you survive going to the nearest resource' as this should almost always pass. In edge cases the unit will die.
[5] Edge case: Optimal path only over resource tiles. Is that even possible?
[6] Edge case: No resources on the map. Default to 'no'.
Unit is out of city + Unit has no free capacity + No city needs refueling + No city can be expanded
